                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18360404-1047-offence-1 t18360404-cd-157"></join>8th of March</rs>, 1 hearth-rug, value 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18360404-name-1064" type="victimName">
